{"type": "article", "id": 3346, "title": "Pininfarina限量版自行车", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-07T07:56:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052326341IpO3DuAqR8LNnS7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利知名汽车设计厂商 Pininfarina 日前推出一款名为「Pininfarina Fuoriserie」的自行车，灵感源自于 1920-1930 年代的复古汽车风格，自行车架采用了全钢结构，车把与车座部分选用了棕色的编织皮革进行包裹，车座前部的横杆则被用胡桃木与石楠木的涂层进行了装饰。此外，Pininfarina Fuoriserie 还配有 LED 照明系统与 Bike+ 电动能源系统，这款复古自行车的手工制作工作全部由意大利老牌自行车厂商 43 Milano 完成，全球限量 30 辆，普通版售价 6000 欧元，电动版售价 9000 欧元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232631dvPpfQLS32tchRU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232631215GRk0sDYOvTQlr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232632BPSfyks3NAVb0XFz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052326329GoOwVY6TUQ4dgX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232633GN7jHWTdYmS9lpIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}